Dear [Employee Name],

We're thrilled to be assisting you with your relocation to London!  Following our initial conversation, we wanted to confirm your upcoming consultation with one of our relocation specialists.

During this call, we'll discuss your specific needs and preferences in more detail, helping you find the perfect accommodation to suit your lifestyle. We'll also answer any questions you may have about the relocation process itself.

We look forward to speaking with you soon!

Sincerely,
The Global Relocation Team
